long_description: Keen Harvest MJ shoes offer truly unique, one-of-a-kind style with each pair, thanks to construction that uses repurposed fabric scraps. Uppers use recycled cotton-either reclaimed rice bags or repurposed fabric scraps-for distinct, fun style; instep strap crosses foot for a secure fit. More subtle than other Keen shoes, but still there-patented rubber Toe Guards protect feet from scuffs, bumps and uneven sidewalks. Cotton canvas linings are soft against bare feet. Removable polyurethane footbeds act as the midsoles to provide cushioning and comfort for all-day wear. Low-profile, nonmarking natural rubber outsoles on the Keen Harvest MJ shoes supply good, all-around traction.
